    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I think it is time to rething about (not for V1):\n- widget instance methods (hide, show, refine from outside?)\n- widget events (hide, show, refine event?)\n- widget public properties (.container?)\n\nBecause your particular need emphasis that this could be handled by a generic API rather than inventing more and more API methods for specific needs.\n\nRef #83 \n\nWhat do you think?\n",
