    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Agreed with @vvo. Next version should have emphasis on event and public methods/properties of container. I feel that this specific use case should be handle by the users, listening to events and interacting with its widgets, but we should give them the flexibility to do so.\n",
